 or contractual obligations. Reviews must not contain financial information. A review must not contain any references to specific amounts of money spent while using the product. Reviews must not accuse or make reports of fraud or any criminal activity. Unless the fraud or activity has been proven by a court of law, we do not allow references to legal matters in our reviews. Our team is not qualified to make a decision as to the truthfulness of a legal accusation."
