      "question": "What is Peer Community?",
      "answer": "Peer Community is a digital community platform for verified members to engage in discussions with peers and share meaningful knowledge in real-time. Members can post their own Q&A open-text threads and Polls, as well as connect and network with each other. Crowd-sourced insights are supported by Gartner- initiated peer Benchmark Surveys and their matching One-Minute Insights reports. Peer Community produces entirely peer-driven, high-quality, and detailed insights in a trusted environment that is meant to eliminate the distractions of self or brand-promotion, sales, and recruiting."
